tor successfully suppresses those specific outliers.\n\n5. **Visualization:** Add a step to visualize the "Volatility Budget" as a stacked area chart over time. This will provide a clear, intuitive view of how the risk composition shifts between the two sub-sectors over the 62-day period.\n\nThe plan is otherwise excellent and avoids unnecessary complexity.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='7983859f-485f-4316-93b8-32dadad9b2af'



